column3: [' (StepDescription: Chop-Chop 1/4 red bell pepper into tiny bits)']
[' (StepDescription: Add-Add 1/3 cup cheddar cheese to a microwave-safe cup)']
[' (StepDescription: Place-Place the chopped pepper in the microwave-safe bowl)']
[' (StepDescription: Add-Add 1 tablespoons of water to the bowl)']
[' (StepDescription: Melt-Melt the cheese by microwaving cup for 30 sec. (Check after 30 seconds and microwave for 10 seconds more if needed).)']
[' (StepDescription: Mix-Mix the cheese and red bell pepper in the bowl)']
[' (StepDescription: Add-Add 1/4 teaspoon pepper to the bowl)']
[' (StepDescription: Add-Add 1/4 teaspoon salt to the bowl)']
[' (StepDescription: add-add 1/2 tbsp softened butter to the bowl)']
[' (StepDescription: Mix-Mix all the ingredients of the bowl well)']
